{"tid":1846641,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港醫院 病人直接倒地訓係走廊","createTime":"2020-01-27T16:40:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T16:44:59.000Z","uid":208505,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f6816edbdef1df27275c4b6168ae559c89df1972","tid":1846641,"uid":208505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T16:40:57.000Z","msg":"網上流傳片段，片中倒地男子剛由開平回到香港，操一口流利普通話並持有香港身分證的人士。根據網上消息指，該名男子情緒不穩定，有精神病紀錄、出現發燒症狀。護士把它分流到隔離病房。根據消息人士指該名病人突然除去保護衣物及口罩，想離開醫院，行為非常危險。<br />\n<br />\n網上片段<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://fbwat.ch/1TtgwEMrdJ1LE174\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffbwat.ch%2F1TtgwEMrdJ1LE174&d=gjA94EiKSJsk9JMrtOnM5ma%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=3608404e\" target=\"_blank\">https://fbwat.ch/1TtgwEMrdJ1LE174</a>"},{"pid":"75d38ef2cacdcb4f7c79ebca0b56c737a4de36e0","tid":1846641,"uid":208505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T16:41:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a55a0f8d863d0fd0e32d791a7986eb2daeea0bf","tid":1846641,"uid":208505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T16:41:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ca6ad14cf0f82945e341cd3e7fe300e916a3913","tid":1846641,"uid":208505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T16:42:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14d44a5123af28444d70fb9ea7dd96f329c224b0","tid":1846641,"uid":208505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T16:42:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04d6baae973ed1b844360281294c8be0524c6be7","tid":1846641,"uid":273466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T16:42:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tVMo4Ha.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtVMo4Ha.jpg&h=7ae197b2&s={SI